annotationA: Mitochondrial ribosomal protein L44; Ribonuclease III activity; structural constituent of ribosome; RNA binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitochondrial translation; RNA processing; neurogenesis
annotationB: Mitochondrial ribosomal protein L55 is involved in mitochondrial biogenesis and cell division; Belongs to the mitochondrion-specific ribosomal protein mL55 family
